# Image Analysis in C++

A C++ project focused on image processing and analysis, including basic operations such as thresholding, resizing, and grayscale manipulation.

## Features

- Image loading (PPM/PGM format)
- Thresholding (seuillage)
- Image resizing
- Basic pixel-level operations

